    "post_content": "<em><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We are looking for a Content Marketing to join our team, enrich our websites with updated content, new blog posts &amp; marketing portfolio.</span></em>\r\n<h3><b>1. Job Description </b></h3>\r\n<i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">(The scope of work include Vietnamese and Japanese)</span></i>\r\n<ul>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Manage social networking sites. Build and manage content (including writing content, presenting content, ideas about images and videos) on social networking sites (Facebook, Twitter, Telegram, etc.) of the company.</span></li>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Write PR articles to send to media partners (press, influencers, co-marketing campaign partners, etc.).</span></li>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Write standard SEO articles for the company's products and services to post on the website under the guidance of the Marketing Manager.</span></li>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Build and create other types of content for each campaign: landing page, email, script for video, advertising articles, FAQs, …</span></li>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Compile available content.</span></li>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Coordinate with the Development Department to build &amp; manage content orientation, image, strategy of Marketing campaigns.</span></li>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Join the team to build and manage Marketing campaigns, contribute creative ideas to the digital marketing campaigns.</span></li>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Expand untapped communication channels (if any)</span></li>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Perform other tasks as required by the manager.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3><b>2. Compensation &amp; Benefits</b></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Saturday &amp; Sunday OFF, Overtime pay is 150%, 200%, 300% as per labor law;</span></li>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Salary review 2 times/ year, based on work performance and company’s performance;</span></li>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Performance bonus, 13th- month salary, public holidays bonus (2/9, 30/4, 1/5, 1/1); bonus for Excellent Employee and Excellent Team;</span></li>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Social insurance, health insurance, unemployment insurance and Bao Viet care insurance;</span></li>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">01 hour paid leave per day for women having children under 12 months</span></li>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Minimum 14 paid leaves per annum for all employees after probation;</span></li>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nice &amp; modern working space with young, dynamic &amp; friendly colleagues and free coffee, tea, drinks;</span></li>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Yearly company trip and year-end party, quarterly team building and weekly eating together; English - Japanese Club, Sports Clubs;</span></li>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Men’s Day, Women’s Day, Children’s Day, Mid-Autumn Festival and other benefits under the provisions of the company;</span></li>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Flat, open and sharing culture with friendly management team; outsourcing company with product mindset;</span></li>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Training courses and working opportunities with technical gurus who built and operated world-class applications with millions of users. This might be a good chance for graduated students to learn cutting-edge technologies and how to build scalable system from scratch;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3><b>3. Requirements</b><b>\r\n</b></h3>\r\n<i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Must have</span></i>\r\n<ul>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Fluent in Japanese (N2 or above)</span></li>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">At least 1 year of experience as a Content Marketing, Copywriter or similar role.</span></li>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Experience working with media partners such as producers, agencies, newspapers, influencers….</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nice to have</span></i>\r\n<ul>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Experience in working for Japanese companies or market, is a big plus;</span></li>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Know how to use softwares such as Adobe Illustrator, Photoshop, Lightroom... is an advantage.</span></li>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Portfolio of published articles</span></li>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Creative thinking to solve problems and have breakthrough initiatives.</span></li>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ability to communicate well with colleagues, discuss, negotiate and listen.</span></li>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Can set goals for yourself and be willing to do them. Ability to do what a manager is going to do, suggest tasks and define what needs to be done, etc .., and do these by yourselves.</span></li>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">BSc in Marketing, Japanese, or related field.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3><strong>4. How to apply</strong></h3>\r\n<div class=\"contact\">Feel free to apply even if you feel like you don’t fully match the description above. Letters of interest and CVs in English should sent electronically to us (<span style=\"color: #00aae7;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #00aae7;\" href=\"mailto:hr@sotatek.com\">hr@sotatek.com</a></strong></span>) with subject \"<strong>Application for Content Marketing</strong>\"\r\nShould you have any queries, please feel free to contact us:\r\nEmail:<strong> <span style=\"color: #00aae7;\"><a style=\"color: #00aae7;\" href=\"mailto:hr@sotatek.com\">hr@sotatek.com</a></span></strong>\r\nFB Fanpage: <span style=\"color: #00aae7;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #00aae7;\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/SotaTek-Recruitment-103449144861080\">SotaTek Recruitment</a></strong></span>\r\nTel: 024-6672-2259</div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;",
