    "post_content": "<h3><b>1. Job Description</b></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Control, evaluate the implementation of compliance with the prescribed process of projects at the departments according to their standards;</span></li>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Control progress, warn and detect problems that may affect the project progress;</span></li>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Synthesize, make statistics, analyze and report data according to required standards; thereby presenting risks, problems and recommendations for implementation;</span></li>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Perform tasks related to process management as assigned by the department leader/head of the department;</span></li>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Support the projects to comply with the software development process according to the Agile - Scrum model;</span></li>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Participate in the development and implementation of CMMi and periodic ISO audit;</span></li>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Support training activities; Consult and propose to build a process suitable to the actual projects.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3><b>2. Compensation &amp; Benefits</b></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Saturday &amp; Sunday OFF, Overtime pay is 150%, 200%, 300% as per labor law;</span></li>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Salary review 2 times/ year, based on work performance and company’s performance;</span></li>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Performance bonus, 13th- month salary, public holidays bonus (2/9, 30/4, 1/5, 1/1); bonus for Excellent Employee and Excellent Team;</span></li>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Social insurance, health insurance, unemployment insurance and Bao Viet care insurance;</span></li>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">01 hour paid leave per day for women having children under 12 months</span></li>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Minimum 14 paid leaves per annum for all employees after probation;</span></li>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nice &amp; modern working space with young, dynamic &amp; friendly colleagues and free coffee, tea, drinks;</span></li>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Yearly company trip and year-end party, quarterly team building and weekly eating together; English - Japanese Club, Sports Clubs;</span></li>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Men’s Day, Women’s Day, Children’s Day, Mid-Autumn Festival and other benefits under the provisions of the company;</span></li>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Flat, open and sharing culture with friendly management team; outsourcing company with product mindset;</span></li>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Training courses and working opportunities with technical gurus who built and operated world-class applications with millions of users. This might be a good chance for graduated students to learn cutting-edge technologies and how to build scalable system from scratch;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3><b>3. Job requirements</b></h3>\r\n<strong><i>Must have</i></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">University degree in Informations Technology or related field;</span></li>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Minimum one year professional experience in QA in software outsourcing companies; </span></li>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Understanding of software development life cycle and project management</span></li>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Knowledge of CMMI, ISO 27000, ISO 9000 and ability to apply to work</span></li>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Good ability to data collection and analysis</span></li>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Good skills in time management, planning, document compiling</span></li>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Good communication skill and teamwork</span></li>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Logical thinking and attention to detail</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong><i>Nice to have</i></strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Good at English</span></li>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Understanding of 5 Why, Fishbone, CAR, Control Chart, Cause &amp; Effect Diagram, Pareto Chart, Scrum process</span></li>\r\n \t<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Proactive seeks learning opportunities beyond current requirements.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 class=\"title\"><strong>4. How to apply</strong></h3>\r\n<div class=\"contact\">Feel free to apply even if you feel like you don’t fully match the description above. Letters of interest and CVs in English should sent electronically to us (<span style=\"color: #00aae7;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #00aae7;\" href=\"mailto:hr@sotatek.com\">hr@sotatek.com</a></strong></span>) with subject \"<strong>Application for PQA</strong>\"\r\nShould you have any queries, please feel free to contact us:\r\nEmail:<strong> <span style=\"color: #00aae7;\"><a style=\"color: #00aae7;\" href=\"mailto:hr@sotatek.com\">hr@sotatek.com</a></span></strong>\r\nFB Fanpage: <span style=\"color: #00aae7;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #00aae7;\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/SotaTek-Recruitment-103449144861080\">SotaTek Recruitment</a></strong></span>\r\nTel: 024-6672-2259</div>",
